Check pasted content for security issues

Usage: tirith paste [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --shell <SHELL>    Shell type for tokenization [default: posix]
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format (default: human) [possible values: human, json]
      --non-interactive  Force non-interactive mode
      --interactive      Force interactive mode
      --html <HTML>      Path to clipboard HTML for rich-text paste analysis
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  echo "suspicious" | tirith paste
  tirith paste --format json < clipboard.txt
